  "description": "<blockquote>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一美人兮，见之不忘。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一日不见兮，思之如狂。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&mdash;&mdash;司马相如 《凤求凰》</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人类的情感总是相似处，就像是英语里也有很多表达思念的短语。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有趣的是，它们很多都有着&ldquo;渴望&rdquo;的含义，来看看呗。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/20/cd44ef6e2e41c68b2924b5837c1f9bca.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. think of</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它的本义是&ldquo;想出；发明&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">We'll have to think of a pretty good excuse for being late.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们得想一个很好的迟到的借口。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">think of也可以表示&ldquo;想念&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">To&nbsp;think&nbsp;of&nbsp;you&nbsp;makes me old.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">思君令人老。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">She could think of nothing but Edward Craddock.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">她一心只思念着爱德华&middot;克雷杜克。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. be concerned with/about</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">concerned做形容词表示&ldquo;担心的；忧虑的；挂念的&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I'm a bit concerned about/for your health.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我有点担心你的健康。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I am concerned with you&nbsp;terribly!</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我好想你！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. cherish&nbsp;the&nbsp;memory&nbsp;of</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">cherish&nbsp;the&nbsp;memory&nbsp;of one's dead mother</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">怀念先母</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I shall evermore&nbsp;cherish&nbsp;the&nbsp;memory&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;patriotic poet.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我将永远怀念这位爱国诗人。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4. long for</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家都了解long的形容词意思，它也有动词含义&ldquo;渴望&hellip;；渴望做&hellip;&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">She longed to see him again.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">她很想再见到他。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I'm longing for news of him.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我正在盼望着得到他的消息。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I cannot conceal from you that sometimes I&nbsp;long&nbsp;for&nbsp;you dreadfully.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我不能对你隐瞒，我有时思念你心焦如焚。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">5. languish for</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>languish</strong>表示<strong>&ldquo;受苦，经历苦难，受煎熬&rdquo;</strong>，languish for的含义是<strong>&ldquo;因渴望而苦恼&rdquo;</strong>。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">He languished for home.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他苦苦地思念家乡。</span></p>\n\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">6. sigh for</span></span></strong></div>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">sigh意思是&ldquo;叹息；惋惜&rdquo;，在我们思念对方而又无法相见的时候，也是会常常哀叹吧。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Spring Festival is drawing near.The Chinese students abroad&nbsp;sigh&nbsp;for&nbsp;home and friends.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">春节将至，海外的中国留学生思念家乡和朋友。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The old man sighed for the good old days.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">老人十分思念过去的美好日子。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">7. pine for</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个短语表示&ldquo;渴望得到&hellip;；苦苦思念&rdquo;。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">He's still pining for his ex-girlfriend.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他还在苦苦地思念着他的前女友。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">值得一提的是，<strong>pine作动词也表示&ldquo;消瘦；憔悴；衰弱&rdquo;</strong>，有没有为伊消得人憔悴的feel！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">8. yearn for/after</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Despite his great commercial success he still yearns for critical approval.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">尽管他获得了巨大的票房成功，但还是渴望得到评论家的认可。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">I shall yearn for you very much.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我会很想你。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/20/c83e4ea477f15f77989e4f9e30d27d86.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然谈到了这么多表达思念的短语，但我还是觉得，我们的中华成语更能一语道破思之如狂的心境。</span></u></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">魂牵梦绕</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【释义】形容万分思念。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【出处】宋&middot;刘过《醉太平》词：&ldquo;思君忆君，魂牵梦萦，翠销香暖云屏，更哪堪酒醒。&rdquo;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【翻译】<strong>I yearn&nbsp;for you&nbsp;by day and dream&nbsp;of you&nbsp;at night. 我很想你，魂牵梦绕。</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一日三秋</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【释义】一天不见面，就像过了三个季度。形容思念人的心情非常迫切。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【出处】《诗经&middot;王风&middot;采葛》&ldquo;彼采葛兮，一日不见，如三日兮！彼采萧兮，一日不见，如三秋兮！彼采艾兮，一日不见，如三岁兮！&rdquo;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【翻译】<strong>a day's separation seems as long as three years&mdash;absence makes the heart grow fonder; miss sb very much</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">朝思暮想</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【释义】从早到晚思念不已。形容非常想念或经常想着某一件事。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【出处】宋&middot;柳永《倾杯乐》词：&ldquo;朝思暮想，自家空恁添情瘦。&rdquo;明&middot;冯梦龙《警世恒言》卷二十四：&ldquo;再说沈洪自从中秋夜见了玉姐，到如今朝思暮想，废寝忘餐。&rdquo;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【翻译】<strong>yearn for/miss day and night; long for sb/sth all day long</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">望眼欲穿</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【释义】眼睛都要望穿了，形容盼望殷切。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【出处】唐&middot;白居易《寄微之》诗：&ldquo;白头吟处变，青眼望中穿。&rdquo;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【翻译】<strong>keep gazing anxiously till one's eyes are strained&mdash;look anxiously forward to; await with great anxiety</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">望穿秋水&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【释义】形容对远地亲友的殷切盼望。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【出处】元&middot;王实甫《西厢记》第三本第二折：&ldquo;望穿他盈盈秋水，蹙损他淡淡春山。&rdquo;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【翻译】<strong>have long been looking forward with eager expectancy</strong></span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1217604/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1217604\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1207801/\">如何一个人练口语？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1013858/\">有声双语美文：我没见过他，他也没有见过我</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219421/\">Quora精选：什么让你内心很强大？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219992/\">《纸牌屋》取消续订，只因男主性侵丑闻曝光！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219911/\">如何立刻结束一段没营养的对话？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1220013/\">表情包还能出错？Google的汉堡竟弄错顺序！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219912/\">这是我20年里看过最奇特的电影，没有之一</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1218501/\">双语美文：时间再少，也要挤出来读书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219990/\">哈里王子和梅根竟然是远方表亲？这不是在逗我！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1219684/\">美国开始山寨中国的东西了，风水轮流转</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
